Help Type: command
Command: wikigraph wkg-job://<job-id>/target set

Purpose:
  Change the task of an existing active job.

Usage:
  wikigraph wkg-job://<job-id>/target set <reading-graph|reading-summary|knowledge-graph>

Arguments:
  <job-id>              Full job id or an unambiguous prefix.

Task choices:
  reading-graph         Build only the Reading Graph.
  reading-summary       Build the Reading Graph summary path.
  knowledge-graph       Build entity mentions for entity search.

Examples:
  wikigraph wkg-job://75d12f7e/target set reading-summary
  wikigraph wkg-job://75d12f7e/target set knowledge-graph
